<figureCitation box="[1018,1082,310,331]" captionStart="FIGURE 4" captionStartId="6.[151,250,914,936]" captionTargetBox="[213,1377,525,863]" captionTargetId="figure@6.[209,1381,519,863]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="FIGURE 4. Surfaces between larger punctures in the pronotum: a) densely, minutely punctate (Pachysquamus subcostulatus), b) not punctate (Scierus and Hylastes), c) with smaller punctures about half the size of larger (Hylurgops)." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/252618/files/figure.png" pageId="7" pageNumber="308">
Fig. 
<number box="[1068,1082,310,331]" pageId="7" pageNumber="308" value="4.0">4</number>
</figureCitation>
